node.text: Ideally you’d discover and discuss these topics during the dating stage, but very few actually do. What would you add to this list? 🤔

Spend less, Invest more = GROW money

Spend more, Invest less = LOSE money
Let me know in the comments :)

node.text: Stop looking for external validation to get started and just get started. Give yourself permission to start and stay focused! 💯
You can’t control your money if you can’t control your emotions. 💯

The money itself has never been the goal.

The goal has always been FREEDOM. Time freedom, location freedom, and financial freedom.

Be the person with $100k in the brokerage account and a $10k car. 

Not a $100k car with only $10k in the brokerage account.
